title: Southwest Florida Regional Ecosystem Restoration Plan Boundary
name: Southwest Florida Regional Ecosystem Restoration Plan Boundary
description: This GIS data set contains Florida county boundaries found on the most recent 7.5-minute USGS (1:24000 scale) quadrangles available in 1997. The county borders extend to the state water line. The shoreline linework matches that of FMRI 1:40K shoreline. Counties were selected that will be in the plan, from levey to Collier. We backed out the area in Levy that that was not in SWFWMD.
